      IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
         PROGRAM-ID. GREATEST-OF-THREE.
         AUTHOR HAWIN.
  
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
         CONFIGURATION SECTION.
           SOURCE-COMPUTER. IBM-3278.
           OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-3278.
    
       DATA DIVISION.
         WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
         01 NUM1 PIC 9(4).
         01 NUM2 PIC 9(4).
         01 NUM3 PIC 9(4).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           DISPLAY "GREATEST-OF-THREE-PROGRAM RUNNING...".
    
           ACCEPT NUM1.
           ACCEPT NUM2.
           ACCEPT NUM3.
    
           IF NUM1 > NUM2
             IF NUM1 >NUM3
               DISPLAY 'NUM1 : 'NUM1 ' IS THE GREATEST'
             ELSE
               DISPLAY 'NUM3 : 'NUM3 ' IS THE GREATEST'
             END-IF
           ELSE
             IF NUM2 > NUM3
               DISPLAY 'NUM2 : 'NUM2 ' IS THE GREATEST'
             ELSE
             DISPLAY 'NUM3 : 'NUM3 ' IS THE GREATEST'
             END-IF
           END-IF.
  
           STOP-RUN.
